WEBVTT

00:00.711 --> 00:02.327
<i>Previously on "Bitten".</i>

00:02.328 --> 00:03.552
Jeremy stepped down.

00:03.553 --> 00:05.272
Elena has control of the Pack.

00:05.297 --> 00:07.164
Anyone has the right to challenge.

00:07.166 --> 00:10.333
If you choose to stay I
won't demand your loyalty.

00:10.335 --> 00:12.836
- I'll promise you mine.
- You're my Alpha.

00:13.973 --> 00:15.539
Where are the men? Get them in here!

00:15.541 --> 00:17.240
No one is here to help you, father.

00:17.242 --> 00:18.642
This is your fate.

00:19.679 --> 00:21.079
(SCREAMING)

00:21.080 --> 00:22.512
- (GRUNTING)
- (FLESH RIPPING)

00:22.514 --> 00:26.383
My brothers, this is the
man who killed your Alpha.

00:26.385 --> 00:28.185
Now we can exact our revenge.

00:28.187 --> 00:31.521
This wire is now where
nerves connect to uterus.

00:31.523 --> 00:34.558
I can make this 1000 times
worse than childbirth.

00:34.560 --> 00:36.560
- (BUZZING)
- (HIGH-PITCHED SCREAM)

00:36.562 --> 00:38.695
(ROARING)

00:40.531 --> 00:43.199
HAIGHT: Elena, you can't
Change for a little while.

00:43.201 --> 00:44.901
You risk tearing your uterine wall,

00:44.903 --> 00:46.569
the internal bleeding could kill you.

00:46.571 --> 00:51.207
_

00:51.209 --> 00:53.409
ELENA: Roman killed her, not you.

00:53.411 --> 00:54.910
SASHA: I broke the rules,

00:54.912 --> 00:57.079
Natalya should never
have known what I was.

00:57.081 --> 00:58.747
That's why we keep secrets,

00:58.749 --> 01:01.650
because the truth changes everything.

01:01.652 --> 01:06.688
♪

01:06.690 --> 01:10.058
ELENA'S VOICE: <i>If they knew
what the future might hold,</i>

01:10.993 --> 01:14.261
<i>they'd look at me differently.
They'd be afraid.</i>

01:14.265 --> 01:15.665
RADIO HOST: <i>In local news, our top story</i>

01:15.666 --> 01:20.035
<i>is the discovery of the body of slain
State Trooper Anthony Rafalski</i>

01:20.037 --> 01:21.903
<i>in addition to the recent disappearance</i>

01:21.905 --> 01:24.072
<i>of former Sheriff Karen Morgan.</i>

01:24.074 --> 01:25.974
<i>Sam Talbot, Mayor of Bear Valley,</i>

01:25.976 --> 01:28.176
<i>will be speaking out at
noon tomorrow at City Hall</i>

01:28.178 --> 01:31.078
<i>to address citizen concerns
about local safety.</i>

01:31.080 --> 01:33.414
ELENA'S VOICE: <i>There's a part of
me that wants to tear it all down.</i>

01:33.416 --> 01:36.618
<i>Fate is pushing us in this direction.</i>

01:36.620 --> 01:39.154
<i>It has been, all along.</i>

01:39.156 --> 01:45.156
♪

